pub fn with_transaction_result<R,
                               impl FnOnce() -> Result<R, DispatchError>: FnOnce()
                               ->
                               Result<R,
                                      DispatchError>>(impl FnOnce() -> Result<R, DispatchError>)
-> Result<R, DispatchError>
defs.docs: Execute the supplied function in a new storage transaction.

attributes.value: / Execute the supplied function in a new storage transaction.
/ All changes to storage performed by the supplied function are discarded if
/ the returned outcome is `Result::Err`.
/ Transactions can be nested to any depth. Commits happen to the parent
/ transaction.
